Background

The report of this analysis refer to two articles: - Prognostic and predictive value of a microRNA signature in adults with T-cell lymphoblastic lymphoma - A CpG Methylation Classifier to Predict Relapse in Adults with T-Cell Lymphoblastic Lymphoma
